The Pytrol is a very simple web interface for interation with FUNC (Fedora Unified Network Controller).
It's a zero-conf (could change in the future) and database-free system, built using only FUNC/certmaster API.

Dependencies:
- Python: http://www.python.org/
- webpy: http://webpy.org/
- FUNC: https://fedorahosted.org/func/

Screenshots:
- pytrol-screenshot.png

Examples:
- examples/apache.conf: Integrating Pytrol and Apache web server (+ mod_fastcgi).

